    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "皇帝亚罗拉斯和绯龙在火山深处交战。\\n塞西娅一边观望战局，一边等待哥哥的到来。\\n为了解救塞西娅，\\n王子赶往火山最深处。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "在阿德拉火山，有个自称皇帝的男人。\\n听闻此事，\\n我们一行人马不停蹄地赶往火山。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "据说外表和父亲一模一样的那个男人，\\n要讨伐栖息在阿德拉火山中的\\n传说中的六龙之一“绯龙”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "火山突然喷发，\\n是否与绯龙之怒有关呢？\\n必须阻止皇帝，救出塞西娅才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "大地如痛苦挣扎般地摇晃，\\n古老的火山不停地咆哮。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "阿德拉火山。\\n“传说中的六龙”之一\\n——“绯龙”的居所。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "如今那座火山\\n仿佛在回应主人绯龙的感情一般，\\n暴怒、发狂……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n阿德拉火山\\n熔岩洞窟   深处\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "哇！快、快跑啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "绯龙",
            "context": "嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝",
            "context": "杂兵果然没什么用……\\n不愧是“绯龙”，名不虚传。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝",
            "context": "怎么了？巫女……\\n你还真老实啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝",
            "context": "已经接受了自己的命运，放弃挣扎了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不，我十分坚信。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你犯下如此暴行，\\n哥哥一定会给予你们严厉的制裁。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "不愧是伊莉雅的巫女！\\n多么坚强的内心，\\n这才是合格的王族！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝",
            "context": "哈尔，你玩笑开过头了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100012_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝",
            "context": "算了。\\n巫女，用你的双眼好好见证\\n绯龙臣服在我力量之下的样子吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n阿德拉火山\\n入口\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "喂喂！阿德拉火山内部\\n应该是往这边走吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是的！\\n从这里冲进去应该就能到达！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "居然要冲入喷发的火山，\\n真是个乱来的王子啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "各位，对不起了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是，如果塞西娅就在火山里面，\\n那我无论如何都要去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "没错！如果塞西娅在，\\n不论火山喷发还是狂风暴雨都无所谓！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "我们一起去接她吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_03_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}